[normal]Q3. What should the Government's aims be for the release of open data?[bold]a. Are the Government's stated key outcomes in its Open Data Strategy the right ones?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
