[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q6. Is open data presented well and of adequate quality?[bold]a. Are the formats of the data being published accessible, useable and[bold]understandable to the public?[bold]b. What metadata is needed to make releases useful?[bold]c. Who will use the data released?[bold]&#xa0;
